title: Ah-mu Tuimalealiifano
text: Ah-mu Tuimalealiifano (born 30 May 1996) is a <a href="Samoans">Samoan</a>-born, <a href="Australian%20people">Australian</a> <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player who played for the in the <a href="Super%20Rugby">Super Rugby</a> competition. His position of choice is <a href="Rugby%20union%20positions">wing</a>.
